---
// Download / CTA section for Orbit AI marketing site
---

<section id="download" class="section max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
  <div class="card rounded-3xl p-9 md:p-12 text-center">
    <div class="mx-auto w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/20 to-violet-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
      <span class="text-2xl text-indigo-400 leading-none">↓</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tighter mb-3">Ready to try Orbit AI?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 max-w-md mx-auto">Currently optimized for Windows. Grab the latest release or build it yourself.</p>

    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="https://github.com/jayakrishnanps/orbit-ai/releases" target="_blank" class="btn-primary text-base px-9 py-3.5 justify-center"><span class="text-lg leading-none">↓</span> Download Windows EXE Installer (via Releases)</a>
      <a href="/orbit-ai/OrbitAI.exe" download class="btn-secondary text-base px-7 py-3.5 justify-center">Direct Download Portable EXE (from this site)</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/jayakrishnanps/orbit-ai" target="_blank" class="btn-secondary text-base px-7 py-3.5 justify-center"><span class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest">GH</span> View source on GitHub</a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 pt-7 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col items-center gap-2 text-xs text-zinc-500">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <span class="text-amber-400">!</span>
        <span>Requires a free Groq API key (get one at <a href="https://console.groq.com/keys" target="_blank" class="underline hover:text-zinc-300">console.groq.com/keys</a>)</span>
      </div>
      <div>MIT licensed • Build with <code class="text-[10px] bg-black/40 px-1 rounded">npm run make</code> after cloning</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
